Sales Dashboard 2

The Sales Performance Dashboard is an interactive business intelligence solution developed in Microsoft Excel to analyze sales, profit, customer orders, and regional performance. The dashboard consolidates data from multiple datasets and presents key business metrics through dynamic charts, Pivot Tables, and interactive slicers, enabling users to make informed, data-driven decisions.

This project demonstrates how Excel can be used as a powerful analytics and reporting tool for business performance monitoring.

🎯 Objectives
Monitor overall sales and profit performance.
Analyze monthly sales and profit trends.
Identify the most profitable states and product categories.
Evaluate regional sales distribution.
Track order returns and shipping performance.
Build an interactive dashboard for business reporting.
